sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User Browser
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OSOAuth as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as Ray Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Node<br/>10001/TCP gRPC
    participant RayWorker as Ray Worker Node<br/>10001/TCP gRPC
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant CASecret as CA Secret<br/>(K8s Secret)

    Note over User, Dashboard: Flow 1: RayCluster OAuth Dashboard Access (OpenShift)

    User->>Router: GET /dashboard<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    Router->>OAuth: Reencrypt TLS<br/>HTTPS/8443
    OAuth->>OSOAuth: OAuth delegation<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+
    OSOAuth-->>OAuth: Auth token validated
    OAuth->>Dashboard: Proxied request<br/>HTTP/8265 (loopback)
    Dashboard-->>OAuth: Dashboard response
    OAuth-->>Router: HTTPS response
    Router-->>User: HTTPS response

    Note over RayHead, CASecret: Flow 2: Ray mTLS Inter-Node Communication

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note right of RayHead: Init Container (create-cert)
        RayHead->>K8sAPI: Get CA Secret<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>RayHead: CA key + cert
        RayHead->>RayHead: Generate node cert<br/>openssl (RSA 2048)
        RayWorker->>K8sAPI: Get CA Secret<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>RayWorker: CA key + cert
        RayWorker->>RayWorker: Generate node cert<br/>openssl (RSA 2048)
    end

    rect rgb(245, 255, 245)
        Note right of RayHead: Runtime Communication
        RayHead->>RayWorker: Ray task/object<br/>gRPC/10001, mTLS
        RayWorker-->>RayHead: Result<br/>gRPC/10001, mTLS
        RayWorker->>RayHead: Heartbeat<br/>gRPC/10001, mTLS
    end

    Note over User, RayHead: Flow 3: Ray Client Access (OpenShift)

    participant Client as Ray Client SDK

    Client->>Router: Ray client connect<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS passthrough
    Router->>RayHead: Passthrough<br/>gRPC/10001, mTLS
    RayHead-->>Router: Response<br/>gRPC/10001, mTLS
    Router-->>Client: Response<br/>HTTPS/443
